Title: The exact formula for neutrino oscillations

Authors: Massimo Blasone, Peter A. Henning, Giuseppe Vitiello

Comments: 7 pages, RevTeX, revised version

changesJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B451 (1999) 140-145

We present the exact formula for neutrino oscillations. By resorting torecent results of Quantum Field Theory of fermion mixing, we work out theGreen's function formalism for mixed neutrinos. The usual quantum mechanicalPontecorvo formula is recovered in the relativistic limit.